So the IPCC said

100
0:04:42.33,000 --> 0:04:44,000
that we might see significant breakup

101
0:04:44.33,000 --> 0:04:47,000
of the arctic ice in 2100, in their worst case scenario.

102
0:04:47.33,000 --> 0:04:5,000
Actually, if current trends continue,

103
0:04:50.33,000 --> 0:04:52,000
